Package lazyTrees

Class LazySearchTree<E extends java.lang.Comparable<? super E>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • lazyTrees.LazySearchTree<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable
    public class LazySearchTree<E extends java.lang.Comparable<? super E>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    Implements BST with lazy deletion to keep track of total inventory ("deleted" + non deleted) and current inventory (non deleted only).
